name: VocabMax
tag_list: vocabulary, vocab, cat, free, online, gre, sat, gmat, english
overview:
VocabMax is a tool for improving your vocabulary.

What is this? Vocabulary is an important tool required to express yourself effectively. It becomes even more crucial while appearing for GRE GMAT CAT SAT like exams. It has been proved that people remember things more when they are asked as a question. Vocabmax helps you improve your vocabulary by quizzing, and helps you find and learn unfamiliar words with their correct usage.

For Whom? VocabMax is for anyone who want to improve their vocabulary, in particular to those planning to appear an exam like GRE GMAT CAT SAT that requires strong vocabulary. It will also be useful to working professionals, who can’t open a book and read in office. Just steal a minute or two from your work and learn few more words. We keep track of your history, so that you don’t spend time again on the same word the next time you come to us.
